   [EnableDetailedObservability] is set to [True] in [MetricsConfig], metrics are scraped from the \
   container's Prometheus endpoint. If this configuration is not provided, the default path \
   [/metrics] on port [8080] is used with a default publishing frequency of [60] seconds. For \
   first-party and Deep Learning Containers (DLC), the endpoint path is determined automatically \
   and this configuration is optional.\n"]

