         and container image.\n\n\
        \ With caching enabled, the endpoint caches this data in each instance that it provisions \
         for the inference component. That way, the inference component deploys faster during the \
         auto scaling process. If caching isn't enabled, the inference component takes longer to \
         deploy because of the time it spends downloading the data.\n\
        \ "]
}
