   rollback strategy. You can specify your batches as either of the following:\n\n\
  \ {ul\n\
  \       {-  A count of inference component copies \n\
  \           \n\
  \            }\n\
  \       {-  The overall percentage or your fleet \n\
  \           \n\
  \            }\n\
  \       }\n\
  \   For a rollback strategy, if you don't specify the fields in this object, or if you set the \
   [Value] parameter to 100%, then SageMaker AI uses a blue/green rollback strategy and rolls all \
   traffic back to the blue fleet.\n\
  \   "]

