   creates a new fleet during the deployment while maintaining the old fleet. SageMaker flips \
   traffic to the new fleet according to the specified traffic routing configuration. Only one \
   update policy should be used in the deployment configuration. If no update policy is specified, \
   SageMaker uses a blue/green deployment strategy with all at once traffic shifting by default.\n"]

type nonrec rolling_update_policy = {
