      [@ocaml.doc
        "Specifies whether the configuration is for the cluster's root or secondary Amazon EBS \
         volume. You can specify two [ClusterEbsVolumeConfig] fields to configure both the root \
         and secondary volumes. Set the value to [True] if you'd like to provide your own customer \
