        "The Amazon Web Services Key Management Service (Amazon Web Services KMS) key that Amazon \
         SageMaker uses to encrypt data on the storage volume attached to the ML compute \
         instance(s) that run the processing job. \n\n\
        \  Certain Nitro-based instances include local storage, dependent on the instance type. \
