   image is hosted. Specify a value for this property only if you specified [Vpc] as the value for \
   the [RepositoryAccessMode] field of the [ImageConfig] object that you passed to a call to \
   [CreateModel] and the private Docker registry where the model image is hosted requires \
   authentication.\n"]

