   the {{:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/latest/APIReference/API_Search.html}Search} API.\n\n\
  \ For example, to filter on a training job's [InputDataConfig] property with a specific channel \
   name and [S3Uri] prefix, define the following filters:\n\
  \ \n\
  \  {ul\n\
  \        {-   ['{Name:\"InputDataConfig.ChannelName\", \"Operator\":\"Equals\", \
   \"Value\":\"train\"}',] \n\
  \            \n\
  \             }\n\
  \        {-   ['{Name:\"InputDataConfig.DataSource.S3DataSource.S3Uri\", \
   \"Operator\":\"Contains\", \"Value\":\"mybucket/catdata\"}'] \n\
