      [@ocaml.doc
        "The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model package to describe.\n\n\
        \ When you specify a name, the name must have 1 to 63 characters. Valid characters are \
         a-z, A-Z, 0-9, and - (hyphen).\n\
        \ "]
