         specified by [JobConfigSchemaVersion]. Use [DescribeJobSchemaVersion] to retrieve the \
         schema for validation.\n"]
  job_config_schema_version : job_schema_version;
      [@ocaml.doc
        "The version of the configuration schema to use for the job configuration document. Use \
         [ListJobSchemaVersions] to get available schema versions for a job category.\n"]
  job_category : job_category;
      [@ocaml.doc
